00:47:51,469 --> 00:47:54,147
Faster than Warwick, at 1:46.8.

801
00:47:54,149 --> 00:47:57,227
That's where you're aiming.
That's very high, isn't it?

802
00:47:57,229 --> 00:48:00,989
Benedict Cumberbatch,
you... are leaning forwards.

803
00:48:02,069 --> 00:48:03,827
It won't make my time faster,
will it?!

804
00:48:03,829 --> 00:48:06,707
I haven't got much space
left on here!

805
00:48:06,709 --> 00:48:08,309
Then shorten the time!

806
00:48:09,789 --> 00:48:11,029
You did it in one...

807
00:48:13,029 --> 00:48:14,709
..40...

808
00:48:20,269 --> 00:48:21,469
..7.8.

809
00:48:23,149 --> 00:48:24,549
Oh! So you're not faster.

810
00:48:31,469 --> 00:48:33,749
I can live with that.
It's in the middle.

811
00:48:34,909 --> 00:48:37,627
What I've got here is a list of all
the other people who've

812
00:48:37,629 --> 00:48:39,547
appeared on Star Trek.

813
00:48:39,549 --> 00:48:41,987
If it makes you feel any better,

814
00:48:41,989 --> 00:48:45,107
Jean-Luc Picard, 1:50 dead.
Oh, dear.

815
00:48:45,109 --> 00:48:47,267
So you're faster than he was.

816
00:48:47,269 --> 00:48:51,427
But the previous baddie in the last
film, Eric Bana, 1:47.5,

817
00:48:51,429 --> 00:48:53,107
and that was in the wet.

818
00:48:53,109 --> 00:48:54,627
Phwoar. So Eric Bana is faster.

819
00:48:54,629 --> 00:48:56,667
I can't really find any
comfort at all for you.

820
00:48:56,669 --> 00:48:59,227
I've just got to come back,
you've got to invite me back.

821
00:48:59,229 --> 00:49:01,707
I basically brought you down here
and ruined your day.

822
00:49:01,709 --> 00:49:03,387
Yeah, yeah! I do apologise for that,

823
00:49:03,389 --> 00:49:06,347
because it has been an enormous
pleasure. Likewise, thank you.

824
00:49:06,349 --> 00:49:08,667
Best of luck with the new Sherlock,
absolute joy.

825
00:49:08,669 --> 00:49:10,829
Ladies and gentlemen,
Benedict Cumberbatch.

826
00:49:22,749 --> 00:49:24,987
Now, tonight, we are heading for
Madrid

827
00:49:24,989 --> 00:49:26,947
in three convertible supercars.

828
00:49:26,949 --> 00:49:30,827
