00:49:39,149 --> 00:49:41,469
Anyway, we rejoin the action
the following morning.

833
00:49:47,989 --> 00:49:51,029
'After a hectic night on the
lavatory, we headed off.

834
00:49:52,349 --> 00:49:54,349
'But after just 100 yards...'

835
00:49:55,989 --> 00:49:57,589
