00:50:05,629 --> 00:50:09,627
Hammond, look out for that signpost
dead ahead of you. Hammond, careful.

839
00:50:09,629 --> 00:50:11,787
Block of flats on the right.

840
00:50:11,789 --> 00:50:12,829
Please kill me.

