still be a busy old place.

855
00:51:13,989 --> 00:51:16,109
'However...'

856
00:51:29,629 --> 00:51:30,669
Holy God.

857
00:51:31,869 --> 00:51:32,869
Look at it.

858
00:51:35,029 --> 00:51:36,629
There are thousands of them.

859
00:51:41,269 --> 00:51:44,189
This crash was clearly bigger
than ever I realised.

860
00:51:49,069 --> 00:51:52,589
Still, look on the upside - there's
no-one for Hammond to run over.

861
00:51:55,269 --> 00:51:58,349
'And that thought gave me
yet another brilliant idea.'

862
00:52:00,189 --> 00:52:03,867
Nobody is driving on that road.

863
00:52:03,869 --> 00:52:07,227
So what are you suggesting?
Or that road.

864
00:52:07,229 --> 00:52:12,067
What I'm saying is, we turn this
town into a street circuit.

865
00:52:12,069 --> 00:52:16,347
Ship The Stig out, he sets a time in
a car of some sort

